\cb3 - Execution backed by SLAs, not hope\cb1 \
\
\cb3 For CFOs, this is less about \'93yet another tool\'94 but more about reclaiming margin, tightening cash cycles, and scaling operational discipline without inflating headcount.\cb1 \
