\fs28 \cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 At SSOW Asia 2025, held from October 13 - 16 at One Farrer Hotel, Singapore, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://neoflo.ai/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Neoflo.AI}} had the opportunity to engage with some of Asia\'92s top Shared Services & GCC leaders, and the response was nothing short of phenomenal. The agenda featured leaders from the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/adani-group/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Adani Group}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/ibm/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 IBM}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/unilever/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Unilever}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/nttdata/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 NTT DATA}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/kellanova/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Kellanova}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/siemens/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Siemens}}, and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/takeda-pharmaceuticals/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Takeda}}, each exploring how GCCs are evolving into business enablers, rather than just cost centers.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Amid these conversations, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/neoflo-ai/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 neoflo.ai}}\'92s roundtable on \'93Hybrid Human-AI Workflows in Shared Services: From Pilot to Profit\'94 stood out, drawing an oversubscribed audience and sparking one of the most engaging discussions of the week. Led by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nipunmehra/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Nipun Mehra}}, the session addressed one of today\'92s biggest operational questions: How can shared-service and finance leaders move beyond pilots and deliver measurable ROI through AI?\cb1 \
\
\cb3 As discussions spilled over coffee tables and networking halls, one sentiment echoed across leaders from IBM, Kerry Global, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/jlltechnologies/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Technology by JLL}}, and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/company/delivery-hero-se/"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 Delivery Hero}}: AI success isn\'92t about technology adoption; it\'92s about execution at scale.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 For us at Neoflo, the answer lies in bridging that gap: transforming pilots into profits, workflows into outcomes, and operations into growth drivers.\cb1 \
