\fs28 \cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 Procure-to-pay may look simple, but in practice, it is a key component of unlocking working capital. \cb1 \
\
\cb3 Enterprises have tried ERP upgrades, outsourcing, and automation pilots, yet each attempt with AI has seldom reduced complexity, as execution isn\'92t always coordinated. Invoices arrive in multiple formats, approvals sit in inboxes, and compliance slows execution - the impact is leaving cash idle and finance teams firefighting instead of forecasting.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 At Neoflo, we turn P2P into a source of liquidity and control. Our AI-first execution layer connects procurement, AP, and treasury to reduce invoice cycles from weeks to days, prevent duplicate payouts, and deliver real-time visibility into cash and compliance.\cb1 \
\
