\fs28 \cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 There\'92s been much talk of the MIT NANDA report suggesting that 95% of pilots fail. We, at Neoflo, believe what is missing is a single point of accountability. The tool creators are not accountable for results, and enterprises need coordinated cross-departmental commitment to ensure deployment success. \cb1 \
\
\cb3 So we picked a model where we hold ourselves accountable for the results to our clients. It\'92s simple - for a certain set of processes, it is better to let someone else drive. Outsource the back-office grunt work to us and bring back lean agility to your back office.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 We believe we can deliver up to 70% manual effort reduction, and we get paid only when we commit to quality SLAs. We are sure to beat the traditional service provider on every dimension - throughput, SLA & cost.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 That\'92s Neoflo: 3x throughput, 70% manual effort reduction, and outcome-based pricing. Our in-house experts, in partnership with the best-in-class BPO firms, deliver AI + human combinations like never before. \cb1 \
\
\cb3 Backed by Lightspeed India, Peak XV, and Alter Global, and built by repeat founders and industry veterans, Neoflo should be the first port of call for all that back-office grunt work you need but wish you didn\'92t have to do.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 The AI era needs accountability, and that\'92s what Neoflo delivers. Discover how we\'92re redefining the $100B back-office industry: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://lnkd.in/gupT-Xar"}}{\fldrslt \cf7 \strokec7 https://lnkd.in/gupT-Xar}}\cb1 \
